    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三个男人在酒吧里能做的最蠢的事是什么？</strong><br>——当然是选出一个“牺牲者”去搭讪一个女孩。<br>——谁是牺牲者？<br>——你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/2ba3ef0296713da0aee268a77bce102c.poster.avif?t=1772155901\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/2ba3ef0296713da0aee268a77bce102c.webm?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/2ba3ef0296713da0aee268a77bce102c.mp4?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在朋友们的怂恿下，库泰 决定出手，试图吸引神秘的新面孔 艾希尔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但正如 库泰 的动机并不完全单纯，很明显 艾希尔 也不那么无辜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/de49e5db60a1b047d196eac045c7e9dd.poster.avif?t=1772155901\" width=600 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/de49e5db60a1b047d196eac045c7e9dd.webm?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场简单的邂逅迅速演变成一段无法预料的经历。<br>库泰 开始重新认识自己，探索城市中不为人知的一面，并意识到有些人……也许并不完全是人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时他会与陌生人发生冲突，<br>有时会在矛盾的情感中挣扎。<br>他可能会被某种力量迷住——甚至不惜一切，哪怕是生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/c50a29146be719f4c5635eebb954381d.poster.avif?t=1772155901\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/c50a29146be719f4c5635eebb954381d.webm?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/c50a29146be719f4c5635eebb954381d.mp4?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但——这不正是爱情的感觉吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/131c6248e86c26736ea3e924fa79fa40.poster.avif?t=1772155901\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/131c6248e86c26736ea3e924fa79fa40.webm?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077540/extras/131c6248e86c26736ea3e924fa79fa40.mp4?t=1772155901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段奇异的旅程中，库泰 唯一真正的盟友就是：<strong>你。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由玩家选择推动的动态故事发展</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过150个分支决策</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合运气因素的掷骰子机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色自定义，带来多样化游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4K 高清画质</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家实时引导的动作场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可视化的互动剧情地图</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个选择都会影响的“爱情值”系统</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否能引导 库泰 穿越爱情与恐惧的危险之旅，走向幸福结局？<br>还是让他的命运因你的选择而陷入黑暗？</p>",
